'''Saleh Khan''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0635><U+0627><U+0644><U+062D> <U+062E><U+0627><U+0646>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''<U+015E><U+0101>le<U+1E29> Kh<U+0101>n''') is a village in [[Dust Mohammad Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Hirmand County)|Central District]] of [[Hirmand County]], [[Sistan and Baluchestan Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 195, in 37 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|11}}</ref>  

